Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闹钟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? And the darkness drew its order from the autumn grey ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? I'd rather sit this out and sleep the day away instead ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? My weary eyes a bit too slow indeed ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:01:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? I'd rather sit this out and sleep the day away instead ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? To worry about the emptiness that comes ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? If ever there's a reason to be swept up in the season ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? Of the fallen leaves ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? And if the days grow shorter ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? And the darkness drew its order ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? From the autumn grey ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? I'd rather sit this out ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? And sleep the day away instead ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? My weary eyes a bit too slow indeed ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都不知道昨晚阿尔蒙干了什么破事\NYou won't believe the crap Armen pulled last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他断了我公寓的电\NHe cut the power to my apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\NThat's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没灯  没无线网  啥都没有\NNo lights, no Wi-Fi, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,断了十五分钟\NFor 15 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我当时戴着呼吸器\NAnd if I had been on a ventilator,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定早就窒息而死了  对吧\NI could've suffocated in that time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个医生\NYou're a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没戴呼吸器\NYou're not on a ventilator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢天谢地了  但有可能啊\NThank God for that. But I could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时一片漆黑  我可能会绊倒\NI mean, it was dark. I could've tripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真该起诉他\NI should sue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你要吃的吧\NSorry. Were you gonna eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「愤怒为食量」\NI stress eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着\NOkay, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去问他时\NI go to talk to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怪我又把音乐开到很大声\Nand he claims I was playing my music too loud again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的音乐吵到我时我会戴耳塞\NI wear earplugs when your music irritates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没听到水滴声\NI miss the dripping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没听懂重点  肖恩  好吗\NYou're missing the point here, Shaun, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得敲门  询问\NYou knock. You ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是断了某人的电\NYou don't cut someone's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会敲门的吧\NYou knock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当然会敲啊  正常人都会\NOf course, you would knock. Any normal person would.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我疯了  还是他是个反社会者\NI mean, am I crazy or is he a total sociopath?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该戴耳机\NYou should get headphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耳机\NHeadphones?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样可以降低声音\NThey would eliminate the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白\NYeah. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你对这事如此客观公正\NThank you for being so objective about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实你不如去帮阿尔蒙\NIn fact, why don't you go help Armen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,写我的搬出通知吧\Nwrite my eviction notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  我开车再也不走那条路了\NYeah, and I'll never drive down that street again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相当可怕的回忆\NIt's a pretty bad memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  听着确实如此\NYeah, that sounds pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  徒步旅行会很热吧\NWait, it's kind of hot for a hike, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,徒步旅行就会出汗  很正常\NWe're hiking. We're gonna sweat. It happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都听好  别做傻事\NAll right, don't do nothing stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开收银机  把东西放袋子里\NOpen the register and put everything in the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快  赶紧的\NCome on! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动  钱包  手机  啥都交出来\NDon't move. Give me your wallets, phones, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手放到我能看见的地方\NKeep your hands where I can see 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把钱包交出来\NI said get out your wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快\NDo it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱包  快\NWallet, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没事吧\NIs he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  是从野外基地转过来的\NWe don't know. This is routed through Basecamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖恩在现场\NIt says Shaun was there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他有没有受伤\Nbut it didn't say if he was hurt or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急救人员正在送两名重伤人员过来\NWell, EMS has two critical inbounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在很忙  不方便通话\NTheir hands are a little full to chat right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二十岁  女性\N20-year-old female.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腹部一处枪伤\NSingle gunshot wound to the abdomen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,低血压  心动过速\NHypotensive and tachy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上已输了两升生理盐水\NTwo liters of saline en route.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫艾莉\NHer name's Avery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会照顾好她\NWe'll take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰瑞德  跟我走\NJared, you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,颈部钝伤\NBlunt-force neck injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血氧饱和降到80以下\NOxygen sats just dropped below 80.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气管有挤压伤\NTrachea's crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我插了个喉罩\NI inserted a laryngeal mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但气道还有危险\Nbut the airway is not secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  没受伤吧\NAre you okay? You weren't hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的口咽部位由于惊慌过度而扭曲了\NHis oropharyngeal anatomy is distorted from the confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缺氧性肺气肿  他几乎无法呼吸\NSubcutaneous emphysema. He's barely moving air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他送去病区  马上准备手术室\NLet's take him to a bay, and get me an O.R. now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备四个单位O型阴性血  给她交叉配型\NI need four units O-Negative type and cross her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的左肺有微弱的呼吸音\NShe has decreased breath sounds on her left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给她拍个胸片\NLet's get a chest X-ray on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在这干什么\NWhat the hell is he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪他\NIt's his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都怪他\NThis is all his fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,良     医
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一季    第八集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店员说那人进来后\NYeah, clerk says the guy entered,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喊着交出东西\Nshouted orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显然你们的医生没配合\Nand apparently, your doctor didn't comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩中枪\NGirl gets shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店员用球拍打了持枪者\Nand the store clerk clocks the gunman with a bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们就知道这些  -好  你需要什么\N- That's all we know. - All right, what do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要对持枪者和女孩进行法医取证\NI need forensics on the gunman and the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  有发现了就通知你\NAll right, we'll let you know what we find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察想跟你谈谈\NPolice are gonna want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后你就可以回家了\NAfter that, you can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该留下来帮忙  我的值班才开始\NI should be helping. My shift is just starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在枪击现场  我可没时间绑住你的手\NYou were at the shooting. I don't have time to hold your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢被绑住手\NI don't like my hand being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小口径子弹\NSmall-caliber bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在体内反弹\NThey ricochet inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会造成多处无法预测的枪伤\NThey can cause multiple and unpredictable injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们要做什么\NAnd what do we need to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍胸部和腹部X光片\NChest and abdominal X-rays
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要做创伤重点评估超声\Nand a Focused Assessment Sonogram.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三个单位的O型阴性血\NThree units of O-neg and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来帮忙  梅伦德斯医生\NWe could use your help over here, Dr. Melendez!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事\NYes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\NYou're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:05:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-给他拿件隔离服  -好\N- Get a gown on him. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射入伤在下面\NEntrance wound is down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子弹射入时击断了骨盆\NThe bullet fractured the pelvis on the way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  找到射出伤\NAll right, let's look for an exit wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数到三给她翻身  一  二  三\NWe're gonna roll her on three. One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了\NAll right, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在第二和第三根肋骨之间\NBetween the second and third rib.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有大出血\NShe's hemorrhaging here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫菲去拿超声仪\NHey, Murphy, get us the ultrasound
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看里面情况如何\Nso we can find out what's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创伤重点评估超声仪\NFocused Assessment with Sonography and Trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部无创伤  也无二次受伤的迹象\NNo chest contusions or secondary injuries evident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血氧饱和70\NOxygen sat's 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摄像头无法通过塌陷部分\NI can't squeeze a camera past this collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三号手术室准备完毕  但就这一间了\NO.R. 3 is prepped and ready, but that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他手术室都正在使用中\NWe got a full house right now up in surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-最快也要十五分钟后  -我要手术室\N- Next show time is 15 minutes out. - I could use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得控制出大出血\NI gotta get this bleeding under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们那边情况如何\NWhat's the status on your guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带她去  带中枪的人去\NTake her up. Take the gunshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\NHold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的气道受损严重  都没法做气管切开术\NHis airway's so damaged, I can't even do a tracheotomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有五分钟他就缺氧性脑死亡了\NHe's got five minutes until anoxic brain dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我按压住出血了  我会想办法的\NMine's got pressure. I'll see what I can do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我一起刷手准备手术\NYou're scrubbing in with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把插管插入塌陷的气管下面\NGo ahead and feed the tube under the collapsed trachea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始高流量给氧\NStarting high flow O2.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\NAnd we're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在病患能真正呼吸了\NNow that our patient is actually breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以重新调整和修复了\Nwe can realign and repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持针器穿4-0的缝线\NFour-O on a driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀  海绵钳\NScissors. Sponge stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对病患的看法影响了你的医学判断\NIt's a slippery thing letting your feelings about a patient
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是很危险的\Ninfluence your medical judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有\NI didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我察觉到了  她是受害者\NI get the instinct -- She's a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他是枪手  还是种族歧视者\NHe's a shooter, a racist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们经常不知道自己在干什么\NOften we don't even know we're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会让个人感情影响病患的治疗\NI would never let my personal feelings impact a patient's care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她快流血而死了\NShe was bleeding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他三十秒前才恢复正常呼吸\NAnd this guy just drew his first good breath 30 seconds ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他俩都是重伤\NThey were both critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他快死了  你错了  承认吧\NHe was dying. You were wrong. Own it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你我都知道当时很难做出选择\NYou know as well as I do that that was not an easy call to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我知道  -对\N- Do I? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这清理干净  布朗医生\NClear the field, Dr. Browne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我动手术的地方\NNot my operative field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是手术室  刷手出去吧\NThe surgical field. Scrub out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\NExcuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没你事了\NYou're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离开我的手术室\NStep out of my O.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔  麻烦帮布朗医生脱去装备\NGail, can you please relieve Dr. Browne of her instruments
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫克莱兰医生来协助我\Nand page Dr. Cleland to assist me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是更自在了\NNow, isn't this more pleasant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了脾脏  还要处理哪里\NAside from the spleen, what else are we dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子弹导致她的横结肠在脾曲处\NThe bullet ruptured her transverse colon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了破裂\Nat the splenic flexure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,划为待做事项\NPut it on our to-do list.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的男友为什么认为是你的错\NWhy does her boyfriend think it's your fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子弹刺伤了隔膜\NIt punctured her diaphragm here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射入了后胸部\Nand entered the posterior chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又出血了  夹住肺门\NShe's bleeding again. Clamp the hilum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经夹了  伤太重止不住\NI already did. It's too damaged to hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纱布\NGauze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按住这里  别松手\NHold this right there. Don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\NOh, this isn't gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就像把绞碎的牛肉缝合成牛排\NIt's gonna be like sewing ground beef back into a steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新方案  她只能摘除脾脏保命了\NAll right, new plan -- she's gonna have to live without her spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,护士递手术刀\NNurse to pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我切开时  得用缝线结扎脾动脉\NNeed a ligating suture on the splenic artery while I make the cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在这姑娘的血喷我们一身之前帮我处理好吗\NCan you do that for me before this young lady bleeds out on us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫菲\NMurphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BGM: Infinity by One Hundred Years
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  现在开始修补肠破裂\NOkay, let's move on to the bowel perf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖恩\NShaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地你没事\NAh, thank God you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚听说了早上的意外\NI just heard what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖恩  你没事吧\NShaun. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事  我没受伤\NYes. I wasn't injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上到底发生什么了\NWhat happened this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉亚吃了我的苹果\NLea ate my apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  肖恩  今天早上在商店\NNo, Shaun, at the store this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在商店发生什么了\NWhat happened at the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱包  立刻\NWallet now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\NWhy the hell not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说要把手放在你能看得到的地方\NYou said keep my hands where you could see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的钱包在口袋里\NMy wallet is in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我掏钱包你就看不见我的手了\NYou can't see my hands if
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想英雄救美吗\N-- Are you trying to be a hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个外科住院医师\NI'm a surgical resident --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈的闭嘴\NShut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是做游戏  伙计  我是来真的\NThis isn't a game, man. I'm serious. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上把你该死的手机和钱包放到地上\NPut your damn phone and wallet on the ground right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看见这个了吗  伙计  我不是在过家家\NHey, do you see this, man? I am not playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你该死的手机和钱包放到地上\NJust put your phone and wallet on the damn ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点  伙计  按他说的做\NCome on, man, just -- just do what he says!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你按他说的做\NPlease listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  跪下\NShut up! Just shut up and get on your knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手和膝盖放在地上\NPut your hands and knees on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在把你钱包掏出来\NGet your wallet out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会把你打个稀巴烂  我发誓\NI will shoot your crazy ass, I swear to God. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听见我说话了吗  我会开枪的\NAre you listening to me?! I'll do it! Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听见了吗\NYou hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该回去休息\NYou need to take the rest of the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅伦德斯医生也这么说\NDr. Melendez said that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「为什么」  因为你刚刚经历了创伤性事件\N"Why?" Because you just experienced a traumatic event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这不是我的错  -我知道\N- It's not my fault. - I-I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:11:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉身上多处创伤\NAvery has multiple injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅伦德斯医生让我照看她\NDr. Melendez wants me to monitor her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利姆医生\NDr. Lim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我太过分了\NI was out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不应该跟你理论\NI shouldn't have argued with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一期缝合情况良好\NPrimary enclosure went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几个小时后就可以拔管\NWe'll extubate him in a few hours
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以防止更深层次的脏器损害\Nto prevent any further internal damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那很好\NWell, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实  你要保证他继续稳定恢复\NIt is, and you're gonna make sure he stays that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚你要在重症监护室里看护他\NYou'll be babysitting tonight in the ICU.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我  我今晚不值班\NI'm -- I'm not on call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  那你有空\NGreat, then you're available.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚应该会很清闲\NShould be a quiet night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要注意监测生命体征就行\NJust want to keep an eye on those vitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你永远也不知道什么时候会发生气管撕裂\NYou never know with tracheal tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事就不能交给重症监护室的护士吗\NCan't one of the ICU nurses do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她们没在我的手术室里出言不逊\NBut they didn't lip off in my operating room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他最好明早还活着\NAnd he'd better be breathing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下  为什么肖恩在处理受害者的病例\NExcuse me, but why is Shaun on the victim's case?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我评估过了  他没什么事\NI assessed him, and he seemed perfectly capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你评估了\NYou assessed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思  你问过他感觉如何\NWhat does that mean? You asked him how he was feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:12:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会读心术\NYou psychic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有心理学的高等学位\ND-Do you have an advanced degree in psychology?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不知道他脑子里在想些什么\NYou don't know what's going on in his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在手术室里的时候\NWhen I'm in surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意力是集中在我面前开膛破肚的病人身上\Nmy focus is on the person whose guts are open in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是站我对面的人的心理活动\Nrather than the soul of the person standing across from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且似乎肖恩不会让任何事情影响他工作\NAnd it seems that Shaun doesn't let anything impact his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以和他过目不忘的本事一样\NSo, along with his photographic memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把冷酷无情也算作加分项了\NI'm putting cold-hearted in the plus column.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫菲医生  你知道我为什么找你来吗\NDr. Murphy, do you understand why you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格拉斯曼医生说我得和你谈谈\NDr. Glassman said I had to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何医生在经历了潜在性的创伤事件之后\NAfter any doctor goes through a potentially traumatic --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得先确定\NYou have to determine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是否对医院负有法律责任\Nif I'm a medicolegal liability to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  而且更重要的是\NYes. And, more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个为你提供情感支持的机会\Nit's an opportunity to provide you with emotional support.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉如何\NHow are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这没有苹果\NYou don't have apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我们见面的时候我会准备些水果\NI'll try to have some fruit next time we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会为今天早上发生的事情感到后悔吗\NDo you regret anything about this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在糟糕的事情发生之后\NAfter bad things happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反复回想这些事情是很正常的\Nit's perfectly normal to replay the events,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望自己当时做出了不同的选择\Nwishing you had done things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情已经发生了\NIt already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无力回天\NI can't do things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们谈论这件事会让你感到不安吗\NIs talking about this upsetting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在想什么\NWhat are you thinking about right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身炎症反应综合征\NSystemic Inflammatory Response Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手术很顺利\NThe surgery went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经历了像这样的严重创伤后\NAfter a serious trauma like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机体会产生自我毁灭的炎症反应\Nthe body can develop a self-destructive inflammatory reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肾脏  肝脏  肺脏  心脏\NKidneys, liver, lungs, heart --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中任何一个甚至全部同时开始衰竭\Nany or all of them can start to shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会给她抗炎治疗\NWe'll be giving her anti-inflammatories
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并密切监控\Nand monitoring her closely,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后的二十四小时至关重要\Nbut the next 24 hours are critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  谢谢\NOkay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让她平安挺过来  无论你们用什么办法\NJust get her through this. Whatever you got to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我需要你女朋友的亲属\NYeah, well, I need consent forms
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来签署知情同意书\Nfrom your girlfriend's next of kin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你把她的亲人带过来\NIf you could please get her family in here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越快越好\Nas quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能  我...\NI can't. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道她姓什么\NI don't even know her last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们第一次约会\NIt was our first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在一个约会App上认识的\NW-We met on a dating app.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去爬山\NWe were going hiking,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以她没带钱包和身份证\Nso she wasn't carrying a purse or ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那你不需要待在这\NWell, then, you really don't need to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这世上有人在乎她\NSomeone out there cares about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她死了\NIf she dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他们知道临死前有人陪着她\NI want them to know someone was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会让社工试着联系她的家人\NI'll have social work try to locate her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想待多久都可以\NStay as long as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来干净  干燥  健康\NIt looks clean, dry, and healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的脖子快疼死了\NMy neck is killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滥用药物有多久了\NHow long have you been using?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系吗\NWhat's that got to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对止痛药已经有一定程度的耐受\NWell, you likely built up a tolerance to pain meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你真正需要它们的时候\NNow that you really need them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们就不太管用了\Nthey aren't there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才需要芬太尼\NThat's why I need fentanyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一百毫克  你到底帮不帮我\N100 micrograms. Are you gonna help me or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这没用的\NThat wouldn't be helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会纵容你的坏习惯\NThe worst thing I can do for you is feed your habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到我的纹身了\NYou saw my tattoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在惩罚我\NAnd now you're punishing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我忍受疼痛\NYou want this to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在专业地对你进行治疗\NI'm treating you professionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的是在治疗\NIf you were treating me professionally,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不会这么疼了  对不起  但是我\NI wouldn't be in so much pain. I'm sorry, but I --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的把药给我\NJust give me the damn drugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅伦德斯觉得他负责艾莉的病例没问题\NMelendez thinks that he's okay being on Avery's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不这么认为\NI don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅伦德斯医生或许是对的\NDr. Melendez may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个病例或许眼下是肖恩主要的关注点\NThat case seems to be Shaun's primary focus right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许他是不幸中的万幸\NMaybe his condition is a blessing in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许\NMaybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也或许执着于艾莉的健康状况\NOr obsessing over Avery's health
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是宣泄他负罪感的唯一出口\Ncould be his only outlet for a guilty conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着她饱受痛苦煎熬只会让他感觉更糟\NWatching her suffer could just be worsening those feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  要不这就是一个大问题\NSo, either it's a huge problem
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不就根本算不上是问题\Nor it's not a problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的专业意见\NThis is your professional opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖恩的思维非常独特\NShaun has a very unique mind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且性格十分内向\Nand an incredibly introverted nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你的建议\NWell, thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉  但是没有和他进一步的接触\NI'm sorry, but without a lot more time with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能提供这些建议\Nthat's the best I can offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利姆到底想让我做什么\NWhat did Lim expect me to do --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当她质疑我医疗决策的时候\Nstand there and smile
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在那里面带微笑\Nwhile she called my medical judgment into question?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干等在手术室里看着病人奄奄一息是吗\NYour patient nearly died waiting on that O.R., right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太糟糕了  你到底想让我做什么\NIt was bad. What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让她别折磨我了\NTell her to back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不要  -他就是个十足的\N- No. - He's a complete and utter --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有温柔善良的种族歧视者\NNot one of those nice racists, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我本不应该  -克莱尔\N- I shouldn't have to be -- Claire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要做的就是\NHere's what you have to do --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭上嘴然后按照利姆医生说的做\Nshut up and do exactly what Dr. Lim tells you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是\NBut --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许我们可以轮换\NMaybe we could take turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我照看我的患者\NYou can keep an eye on my patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我照看你的\NI keep an eye on yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的肌酐是1.6\NHer creatinine is 1.6.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受了她这么严重的伤\NMild bump in renal numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肾脏指标轻微升高并不奇怪\Nisn't surprising after all her trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上肯定很糟糕\NThis morning must've been crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上  我邻居莉亚过来吃掉了我的苹果\NThis morning, my neighbor Lea came over and ate my apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那太糟糕了\NThat's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  那是我最后一个苹果\NYes, it was my last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很生我们的房东阿尔蒙的气\NShe was upset with Armen, our landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她放音乐很大声\NShe plays her music very loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给了她一些建议  似乎把她惹恼了\NI gave her some advice. It seemed to anger her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为她走的时候没说再见\Nbecause she left without saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得是你做错了\NAnd you think you did something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是很好的建议\NNo, it was good advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖恩  有时候女人想要的是建议\NShaun, sometimes a woman wants advice,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候她是想向你寻求支持\Nand sometimes she just wants support.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道莉亚想要哪个\NHow can I tell which one Lea wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支持她总不为过\NErr on the side of support.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-并没帮到她  -帮到了\N- That's not helpful. - Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布朗医生  病人呼叫你\NDr. Browne. You're being summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时间了\NAbout time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你费劲挣扎  静脉注射针管都弄掉了\NAll your struggling, you've pulled out your IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些破活难道通常不是护士在做吗\NAren't nurses usually supposed to do this kind of crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们让你念医学院\NThey let you go to med school,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却不敢把真正重要的活托付给你\Nbut they don't trust you with any real responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医院肯定有某个有能力的医生\NThere must be a competent doctor tucked around here somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟谁说我需要的不只是阿司匹林\Nwho tell someone I need more than aspirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-「有能力」  -对\N- "Competent"? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂我的意思\NYou know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古埃及的神  被认为是神和人共同的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊姆霍特普是现代医学之父\NImhotep was the father of modern medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-埃及人  -是啊\N- An Egyptian. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你们的种族长脸了\NGood for your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信过去三千多年来你们的种族\NI'm willing to bet there's even been a couple others
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至出过好几个厉害人物  但猜猜看\Nover the last 3,000 years, but guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说\NOn average,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世上大多数伟大的科技进步\Nyou look at most great technological advancements,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都由骄傲的北欧人民持有专利\Nyou'll find a proud Northern European holding the patent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你今天上午在忙活的事吗\NThat's what you were trying to do this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忙着获得从街角商店偷三十块钱\NGet the patent on stealing 30 bucks
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去买毒品的专利吗\Nfrom the corner store for a drug fix?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢瘾君子吧\NYou don't like drug addicts, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多不喜欢的人\NA lot of people I don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小偷  种族歧视者\NThieves, racists,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暴力流氓\Nviolent punks,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是会治疗他们\Nbut I'll treat 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你老妈是瘾君子吗\NWas your mama a drug addict?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老话题的美妙之处\NThat's the beauty of cliches,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在于通常都是真的  对吧\Nis they're true so often, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对我一无所知\NYou don't know anything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没念大学\NI didn't go to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有平权运动特别照顾  所以没念\NI didn't have no affirmative action to get me in,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:20:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你有\Nbut you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为某个软心肠的自由党人在院长办公室\NAll because some bleeding-heart liberal in the Dean's office
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哭着读你写的有关嗑药贱人老妈的文章\Nteared up reading your essay about your crack-whore mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们都是暴力流氓\NI guess we're all violent punks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当时只需把钱包给他\NAll you had to do was give him your wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的尿量很少\NHer urine output is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别碰她\NGet away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别在这推搡医生\NYou can't be in here shoving my doctors around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我  他  他才是...\NMe? He -- He's the --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-天啊  -她得做血液透析\N- Oh, my God. - She needs dialysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的肾脏衰竭得很快\NHer kidneys are failing fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是器官完全衰竭的第一阶段\NThis is the first stage of total organ failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血液透析已排出了两升的过量液体\NWe removed two liters of excess fluid with dialysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她情况在恶化\Nbut she's getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的胸腔有积液\NFluid's building up in her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的肺也衰竭了\NShe's in pulmonary failure, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,排出她胸腔的积液\NDraining the fluid in her pleural space
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以减少气道阻力\Nwould reduce airway resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  准备给她做胸腔穿刺术\NYeah, let's prep her for a thoracentesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动作得快\NWe're gonna have to work fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去准备胸腔引流\NI'll prep the evac drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得把针放到...\NI'm gonna need you to put that needle right between --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第六和第七根肋骨间\N6th and 7th rib.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要让他动手...\NWait, you're gonna let him do --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  好  小心\NShut up. All right, careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别把针插得太深\NDon't put the needle in too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不能让她...  -气胸\N- We don't want to give her -- - Pneumothorax.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  进去了\NAll right, you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看引出了什么\NNow, let me see what I can pull out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但愿她的情况能稳定\NHopefully she settles down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二氧化碳降了  氧气升了\NCO2's down, and O2's climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能稳住她的肾脏和肺部\NWe can manage her kidneys and her lungs,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多个器官衰竭的最后一步就是心脏衰竭\Nbut the last stop in multiple organ failure would be her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全神贯注她的呼吸压力\NWatch her ventilation pressures like a hawk,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注入心脏保护药物\Npush cardioprotective meds,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况有变就呼叫我\Nand page me if anything changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你是她的英雄吗\NThink you're being her hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上你几乎不懂她\NThe fact is you hardly know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也根本不懂他\NAnd you don't know him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.87,0:23:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧\NGo home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.32,0:24:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了\NOkay, I am done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个满嘴污言秽语的恶毒混球\NHe's a foul-mouthed, spiteful bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  我会让接待员\NNo problem. I'll have the concierge
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你找个更对你胃口的病患\Nfind a patient more suited to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.67,0:24:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不需要医生去照顾他\NHe doesn't need a doctor doting over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.11,0:24:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不想看到我\NHe doesn't want me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.81,0:24:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管\NI don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.27,0:24:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我之前顶撞了你\NI'm sorry I disagreed with you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.76,0:24:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不该像个学生妹那样被人奚落\NBut I don't deserve to be scolded like a school girl
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.38,0:24:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你自负之心受不了半点顶撞\Nbecause your ego can't handle being challenged a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这道歉可真有意思\NThat is some apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有正当理由...\NLook, I had a legitimate --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.20,0:24:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真没意识到问题所在吗\NYou really don't see the problem here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.74,0:24:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么  顶撞你吗\NWhat? With challenging you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.88,0:24:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在是当着两个护士的面顶撞我\NRight now, you are confronting me in front of two nurses.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.11,0:24:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢这样对梅伦德斯吗\NWould you do that to Melendez?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.02,0:24:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者你会等五分钟吗\NOr would you wait five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.15,0:24:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我整个职业生涯都在跟不服我领导的男人打交道\NI have dealt with men undermining my authority my entire career.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.20,0:24:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人何必为难女人\NWe shouldn't do it to one another, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.46,0:24:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就像照顾其他病患一样去照顾他\NNow go take care of him like you would any other patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.27,0:25:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有订单餐厅都会复查\NFood services -- they double-check every order.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.76,0:25:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在找什么\NWhat are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.76,0:25:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-一个苹果  -一个苹果\N- An apple. - An apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.22,0:25:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁会点一个苹果  -我\N- Who's getting an apple? - I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.49,0:25:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不  -肖恩\N- No. - Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.79,0:25:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别管苹果了\NForget the apple, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.21,0:25:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  能单独聊聊吗\NI'm sorry. Can I have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.84,0:25:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖恩\NShaun?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.13,0:25:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.17,0:25:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖恩  防卫心别那么强  好吗\NShaun, there's no need to get defensive, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.73,0:25:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要坐下来吗\NDo you want to sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.50,0:25:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  谢了\NNo, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.54,0:25:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你再跟我说一遍\NI want you to tell me again
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.66,0:25:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今早发生的事\Nexactly what happened this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.20,0:25:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说了今早发生的事\NI told you exactly what happened this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.27,0:25:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但人们告诉你是你的错\NYes, but people have told you that it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.51,0:25:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗\NHaven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.14,0:25:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的行动跟枪击是关联事件\NMy actions and the shooting were associative incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.85,0:25:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是因果关系\NIt is not a causal relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.67,0:25:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我踱步  她中枪\NI paced, and she got shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.16,0:25:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但枪击不是踱步引起的\Nbut pacing doesn't cause shootings,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.42,0:25:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则每次有人踱步\Notherwise every time someone paced,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.76,0:25:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会接着发生枪击\Na shooting would soon follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.77,0:25:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你说得非常好\NOkay, that's a very good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.92,0:26:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人持枪\NWhen someone has a gun
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.83,0:26:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是危险的情况  对吗\Nand it's a dangerous situation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.40,0:26:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想扰乱这种情况  对吗\NYou don't want to upset the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.42,0:26:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想把情况变糟\NYou don't want to make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.62,0:26:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也认为这是我的错\NYou think this is my fault, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.53,0:26:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  那是枪...\NNo, no, it was the shoot--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.99,0:26:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是枪手的错\NIt was the shooter's fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.14,0:26:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你的行动可能造成了影响\Nbut your actions may have contributed to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.86,0:26:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  肖恩  等一下  等一下\NOkay, Shaun, wait a second. Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.94,0:26:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你无法完全控制你的行为\NI know your behavior is not completely in your control,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.47,0:26:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也知道你不是完全无法控制你的行为\Nbut I also know it's not completely out of your control.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.47,0:26:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吗\NIs it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.29,0:26:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  也许你有一点责任\NSo, yes, maybe it is a little bit your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.50,0:26:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也当然有责任\NAnd definitely mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.17,0:26:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至不在场\NYou weren't even there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.52,0:26:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.05,0:26:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在场\NI wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.58,0:26:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能坐下聊吗  就一会儿\NCan we sit down, please, just for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.18,0:26:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖恩\NShaun...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.52,0:27:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说服自己一切都没问题\NI convinced myself that everything was fine
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.83,0:27:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为在这里确实是那样\Nbecause in here, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.17,0:27:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺棒的\NIt's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.26,0:27:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你需要帮助\NBut you need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.81,0:27:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖恩\NShaun...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.04,0:27:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要引导\Nyou need guidance --
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.74,0:27:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远不止我所能给予你的\Nmuch more than I can give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.20,0:27:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该跟我的病患待在一起\NI'm supposed to be with my patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.02,0:27:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该全神贯注地看着她\NI'm supposed to be watching her like a hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.34,0:27:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错\NIt's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.47,0:27:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢她\NI didn't like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.05,0:27:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今早一看见她时  她...\NWhen I first saw her this morning, she just...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.83,0:27:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不...\Ndidn't look...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.05,0:28:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.41,0:28:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想放她鸽子\NI mean, I wanted to blow her off,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.72,0:28:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说我忘了带水\Nso, uh... I said I forgot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.75,0:28:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我设想我们去商店买时\NI mean, I figured we'd go to the store
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.06,0:28:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我假装我忘了带钱包\Nand -- and I'd pretend that I forgot my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.93,0:28:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她没有带钱包  所以...\NI knew she didn't have her purse, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.46,0:28:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有水  我们就不能去远足了  对吗\NWe can't go hiking without water, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.85,0:28:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就无害不罚了\NI mean, no harm, no foul?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.09,0:28:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我她才会去那\NShe was there because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.84,0:28:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会在这...\NShe's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.16,0:28:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我\Nbecause of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.65,0:28:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是因果关系\NIt's not a causal relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.85,0:28:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  你说什么\NWait, excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.96,0:28:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是因果关系\NIt's not a causal relationship --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.66,0:28:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说谎和枪击\Nlying and shootings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.81,0:28:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说谎不会引起枪击\NLying doesn't cause shootings,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.99,0:28:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则  每次有人说谎...\Notherwise, every time someone lied --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.10,0:28:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的脉压变低了\NHer pulse pressure is narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.83,0:28:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  那是什么意思\NWait, what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.73,0:28:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她快死了\NShe's dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.17,0:29:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上呼叫梅伦德斯\NPage Melendez. Stat!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.39,0:29:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的呼吸率上升了\NYour respiratory rate is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.24,0:29:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呼吸有困难吗\NAre you having trouble breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.54,0:29:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  很紧密\NYeah. It's tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.23,0:29:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找利姆医生\NFind Dr. Lim.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.66,0:29:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脉压变低表示心排血量减少\NNarrow pulse pressure indicates a reduced cardiac output.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.48,0:29:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炎症在影响她的心脏\NThe inflammation is affecting her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.40,0:29:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她处于器官衰竭末期\NShe's in end-stage organ failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.81,0:29:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我们可以插入主动脉内球囊反搏\NYes, we can insert an intra-aortic balloon pump.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.78,0:29:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许能减轻她心脏的工作量\NIt may reduce some of the workload on her heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.29,0:29:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但衰竭得很快  非常快\Nbut it's failing fast -- really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.94,0:29:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只需要撑过一夜\NIt only needs to work overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.39,0:29:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后炎症反应会改善\NThe inflammatory reaction will improve after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.26,0:29:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果衰竭得那么快不是因为她的心脏呢\NWhat if it's failing so fast because it's not her heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.13,0:29:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近两次检测\NHer hemoglobin's dropped from 14 to 12
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.81,0:29:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的血红蛋白值从14降到了12\Nbetween her last two draws.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.98,0:29:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她是因为某处有出血呢\NWhat if the real problem is she's bleeding somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.80,0:29:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鉴于她的病情\NGiven what she's been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.74,0:29:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下降两点也许没什么\Na two-point drop could mean nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.05,0:29:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能代表有出血状况\NOr it could mean a bleed,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.56,0:29:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样也能说明脉压为何会降低\Nwhich would account for the narrow pulse pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.37,0:29:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的心脏也会没事了\NHer heart could be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.11,0:30:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你说得对  我们得再给她开刀\NIf you're right, that means we'd have to open her back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.13,0:30:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不确定她的身体是否能够承受第二次手术\NI don't know if her body can handle another operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.08,0:30:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  承受不了\NNo, it can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.22,0:30:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过主动脉内球囊泵治疗心脏衰竭\NTreating heart failure with an aortic pump
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.12,0:30:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是比较简单的手术\Nis also a simple procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.56,0:30:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以咱们现在要根据手术难易度来下诊断了吗\NSo we're going to diagnose based on which procedure is simpler?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.31,0:30:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的猜测没错  她泵不出足量的血\NIf I'm right, there could be no more blood to pump.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.53,0:30:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会死的\NShe'll be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.92,0:30:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她快不行了\NShe's crashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.27,0:30:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以准备介入以进行泵血\NWe should prepare the cath lab for a pump.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.94,0:30:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备手术室吧\NWe should prepare the O.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.67,0:30:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧推她进手术室\NLet's get her into an O.R. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.58,0:30:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血红蛋白降到8了\NHemoglobin's dropped to 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.18,0:30:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她大出血了\NShe is bleeding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.64,0:30:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但出血点在哪儿\NYes, she is, but where?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.05,0:30:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧找到出血点\NGot to find where the bleeder's coming from
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.48,0:30:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她死前钳住出血点\Nand clip it before she dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.46,0:30:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没找到\NI got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.28,0:30:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是藏在腹膜后腔或纵膈后面了\NMust be hidden under the retroperitoneum or mediastinum.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.99,0:30:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开刀的这块区域很大\NThat's a whole lot of real estate
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.98,0:30:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能盲目地探寻了\Nto cut open and just go blindly looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.65,0:30:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先从腹腔开始吧  她的枪伤在那里\NWe should start at the abdomen. She was shot there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.75,0:30:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子弹贯穿了胸腔\NThe bullet passed through the posterior thorax.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.31,0:31:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收缩压40  舒张压无  她快死了  尼尔\NBP's 40 over palp. She's dying, Neil.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.53,0:31:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论你要做什么  赶紧动手\NWhatever you're gonna do, you need to do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.35,0:31:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就到处都查一下吧\NWe need to look everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.30,0:31:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请给我一把手术刀和胸骨锯\NGive me a knife and sternal saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.40,0:31:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要给她开腹  从胸腔直到骨盆\NI'm gonna open her up from chest to pelvis.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.42,0:31:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给胸骨和腹部碘伏消毒\NPrep the sternum and abdomen with Betadine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.75,0:31:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要一把海绵钳\NGonna need a sponge stick
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.78,0:31:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在找到出血点时以便控制\Nto control the bleeding when we find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.70,0:31:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.01,0:31:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从她左侧第二根和第三根肋骨那里下刀\NOpen her between the second and third rib on the left side.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.73,0:31:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子弹划破了左侧肋间最上动脉\NThe bullet nicked the left supreme intercostal artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.05,0:31:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动脉壁破裂\NThe wall has blown.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.24,0:31:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道\NHow do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.25,0:31:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据伤口...\NI followed the injuries --
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.48,0:31:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从骨盆  肠道  脾脏到隔膜\Npelvis to bowel to spleen to diaphragm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.56,0:31:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一个创口就该是左侧肋间最上动脉\NNext target has to be left supreme intercostal artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.91,0:31:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给左侧肋间做术前消毒\NAll right, prep left intercostal space.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.41,0:31:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喘不过气\NI can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.25,0:31:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们不帮帮我\NWhy aren't you helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.30,0:31:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利姆医生两分钟内就会过来\NDr. Lim will be along in just two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.77,0:32:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是医生  赶紧救命啊\NYou're the damn doctor. Do your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.28,0:32:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要打开左侧颈部筋膜间隙\NI need to open up the left neck compartment
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.50,0:32:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,释放压力\Nto relieve the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.94,0:32:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手术包\NProcedure tray?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.05,0:32:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前做过吗\NYou done this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.74,0:32:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\NNope.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.92,0:32:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手术刀\NScalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.53,0:32:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肿胀太厉害\NIt's too swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.33,0:32:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看不到喉结\NI can't see the Adam's apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.56,0:32:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.62,0:32:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沿着颈动脉鞘和气管之间的软凹陷切开\NCut along the soft divot between the carotid sheath and the trachea.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.17,0:32:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,软凹陷\NSoft divot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.52,0:32:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了\NGot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.32,0:33:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况\NUpdate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.72,0:33:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么\NWhat did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.39,0:33:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的颈部有血肿\NHe had a cervical hematoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.84,0:33:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得释放压力\NI had to relieve the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.65,0:33:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗\NHere?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.83,0:33:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氧饱和回升了\NOxygen sats are going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.38,0:33:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这很少见  但术后肿胀会伴随气管破烂\NIt's rare, but post-op swelling can happen with tracheal tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.91,0:33:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们才会在术后24小时内严密观察患者\NThat's why we watch them so closely the first 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.84,0:33:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们到手术室完成这个好吗\NYou mind if we finish this off in the operating room?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.88,0:33:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没看到  肖恩\NI don't see anything, Shaun --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.03,0:33:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有出血  也没有动脉破裂\Nno blood and no arterial tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.73,0:33:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找到位置太高\NYou're too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.76,0:33:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在分叉附近\NIt's near the bifurcation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.66,0:33:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打灯\NGet some light in.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.78,0:33:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了\NI got something.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.85,0:33:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分叉右下方有血涌出\NBlood's pooling right under the bifurcation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.42,0:33:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我止血钳\NClamp now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.48,0:34:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不再心脏衰竭了\NShe wasn't in heart failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.05,0:34:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这意味着她的心脏足够强壮\NThat means her heart is still strong enough
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.25,0:34:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能帮她度过这一晚\Nto get her through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.74,0:34:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我错了\NI was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.20,0:34:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.16,0:34:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你刚刚已经弥补了错误\NAnd you just made up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.61,0:34:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对  杰瑞德\NYou were right, Jared.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.61,0:34:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干得好\NGood work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.26,0:34:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗\NYou know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.49,0:34:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对\NYou were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.19,0:34:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈是有问题\NMy mother had problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.31,0:34:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我无法忍受只是袖手旁观\NSo I couldn't afford to just around
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.71,0:34:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望天上掉大饼\Nexpecting everything to be handed to me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.62,0:35:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是其他拖我后腿的事情\Nor whatever else it is that's holding you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.37,0:35:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我取得了一些成就\NAnd yeah, I got some breaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.88,0:35:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也拼了命\Nbut I worked my ass off.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.37,0:35:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两份工作  两个室友  一步步一路走来\NTwo jobs, two roommates every step of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.14,0:35:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠着这些  我才能站在这个位置拯救你的性命\NAnd that is what got me to the place where I could save your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.95,0:35:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你女儿尚未脱离危险\NYour daughter's not out of the woods yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.41,0:35:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我认为她的状况会一天天转好\Nbut I do expect her condition to improve day by day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.82,0:35:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  医生\NThank you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.58,0:35:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢  -客气\N- Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.26,0:35:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝\NBaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.86,0:35:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我们没陪在你身边\NSorry we weren't here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.53,0:35:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉怎么样\NHow are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.27,0:35:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时没办法去爬山了\NProbably won't be hiking anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.84,0:36:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没谢你呢  你就想偷偷溜走吗\NYou sneaking out before I can thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.03,0:36:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  你没必要谢我的\NPlease, you don't need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.14,0:36:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  有必要\NYeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.58,0:36:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有道歉\NAnd apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.87,0:36:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前误会了你\NI was wrong about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.33,0:36:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你要抛弃我\NI thought you were trying to ditch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.90,0:36:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时...\NI was...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.22,0:36:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你抛弃我\Nhoping you were trying to ditch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.63,0:36:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.14,0:36:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你感觉好点\NWhen you're feeling better,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.21,0:36:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我们能再来一次初次约会\NI'd like a second chance at a first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.86,0:37:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.69,0:37:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是对的\NYou were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.97,0:37:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我公然对你不敬\NI publicly disrespected you,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.53,0:37:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我只能公然对你表示敬重以弥补错误\Nand so I thought it only right to publicly respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.26,0:37:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激从你这里学到的教训\NI am grateful for the chance to learn from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.01,0:37:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你需要这场胜利\NI know you needed this victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.31,0:37:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴你今天拯救了性命\NGlad you saved a life today.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.94,0:37:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他不是纳粹\NJust wish it wasn't a Nazi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.63,0:38:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2号跑道\NLane number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.80,0:38:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曼蒂经常跑那条跑道\NMaddie always took that lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.78,0:38:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会一直缀在我后面跑\NShe would tuck in behind me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.25,0:38:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后200米才会超越我\Nand draft until the last 200 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.70,0:38:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个见不得人的小把戏\NIt was a dirty little trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.85,0:38:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-但很有效  -每次都有效\N- It worked. - Every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.14,0:38:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今都13年了\N13 years ago today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.47,0:38:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.23,0:38:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想她\NI miss her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.88,0:38:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给她一些空间吧\NGive her space, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.64,0:38:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给她一些空间\NGive her space.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.02,0:38:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是在渐渐远离\NShe just drifted farther and farther away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.36,0:38:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做的所有事...\NEverything I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.73,0:38:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都做错了\NI did wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.95,0:38:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你尽了力\NYou did your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.81,0:38:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时\NI was...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.49,0:39:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几乎就是住在你家了\Npractically living at your house back then, and --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.84,0:39:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没有...\NIf I hadn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.25,0:39:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩当时都是青少年\NYou were both teenagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.80,0:39:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都一样的中二\NYou were idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.45,0:39:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你走了好运  她没有\NYou got lucky, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.04,0:39:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我...\NIf I...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.24,0:39:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能多陪陪她...\Nwas there more...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.30,0:39:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我\Nif I...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.10,0:39:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她身边...\Nstayed on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.04,0:39:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当时在他身边\NYou're there for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.17,0:39:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以下是本周的天气预报\NHere's your extended forecast for the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.12,0:39:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先旧金山多云\NStarting off with a little bit of cloud cover in San Francisco,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.81,0:39:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气温降至21度...\Ntemperatures in the low 70s...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.61,0:39:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了周末只有几度\N...just a few degrees as we get closer to the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.99,0:39:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望未来7天能天晴干燥\NExpect dry conditions for the next seven days here --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.56,0:39:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你家有灯\NI, uh, saw your light.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.11,0:40:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.89,0:40:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莱尔说我要道歉\NClaire told me to apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.23,0:40:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你并不希望我说实话\Nbecause you didn't want me to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.34,0:40:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是希望我能支持你的观点\NYou only wanted me to support your position,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.72,0:40:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便你是错的\Neven though it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.81,0:40:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不接受你的道歉\NWell, I don't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.15,0:40:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今早我也许有点反应过度\NI may have overreacted this morning a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.35,0:40:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很诚实  极其诚实\NAnd you were honest -- brutally honest --
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.10,0:40:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你在自己家不应该戴耳塞\Nbut you shouldn't have to wear ear plugs in your own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.48,0:40:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别为了让我好受而说谎\NAnd don't start lying to me to make me feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.53,0:40:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我认识的唯一诚实的人\NYou're the only honest guy I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.34,0:40:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.04,0:40:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  肖恩·莫菲\N...have a good night, Shaun Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.13,0:40:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力不吵醒你\NAnd I will try not to keep you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.18,0:41:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BGM: I'll Be Your Mirror by  Clem Snide
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.13,0:41:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? I'll be your mirror ?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.17,0:41:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? Reflect what you are ?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.33,0:41:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? In case you don't know ?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.68,0:41:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? I'll be the wind ?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.20,0:41:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? The rain and the sunset ?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.39,0:41:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? The light on your door to show that you're home ?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.36,0:41:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 'Cause when you think the night has seen your mind ?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.23,0:41:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天犯了个错误\NI made a mistake today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.61,0:41:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? That inside you're twisted and unkind ?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.89,0:41:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人因此受伤了\NAnd someone got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.60,0:41:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? Let me stand to show that you are blind ?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.87,0:41:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? Please put down your hands ?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.61,0:41:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 'Cause I see you ?


